instruction: Share a true story about an instance of resilience.
output: When I was a teenager, my family was facing a difficult financial situation. We had to cut many of our expenses but, despite the hardship, I still wanted to pursue my dream of attending university. I worked hard, look up scholarships, and applied to any program I could find. In the end, I was accepted to multiple universities and was able to pursue my dream of higher education despite our financial struggles. It was a testament to the power of resilience and hard work.
